on><dc:format>xml</dc:format><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">en</dc:language><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">gez</dc:language><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/saint"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/martyr"/><foaf:gender>male</foaf:gender><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/ontology/pers"/><foaf:name xml:lang="gez">አስከናፍር፡</foaf:name><foaf:name xml:lang="gez">ʾAskanāfǝr</foaf:name><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>According to his hagiography, he was a nobleman of Rome. He was ambushed by a gang of thirteen robbers
